  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    Represents a community chest or a chance card of the Monopoly game.
    Chance
    Represents a space, where the user has to draw a chance card.
    DiceCup
    This class represents a dice cuo, which can be used to roll two dice and return an array with each value.
    Game
    Represents the top-level element of a Monopoly game's state.
    GoToJail
    Represents the space that imprisons a player, sending the player to the jail.
    NeutralSpace
    Represents a space that has no action associated with it.
    Player
    Represents a player and his current state in a Monopoly game.
    Property
    A property which is a space that can be owned by a player.
    Space
    Represents a space (field) of the Monopoly game.
    Tax
    Represents a space, where the player has to pay tax.
